text: YO, zalupeni4 brother from another mother ❤

From day one I wanted to Sail with Awolnation. Even if it meant that I had to Kill my Heroes, I would Jump on Thier Shoulders and jam on with them. But now I'm sitting here like I'm in the center of a Hollow Moon, but I know it's Not Thier Fault. I am part of the Knights of Shame, fighting our Soul Wars in a cascade of sound like a Megalithic Symphony. I'm just Some Sort of Creature, running around like AKIDSTHATNOTALRIGHT. But at this point, All I Need is the new Awolnation album. ﻿
